data.description: **THIS IS THE ONE** Welcome Home! This adorable home in the charming community of Chatham Walk is ready for its new family/owners to put their own personal touches to make it home! From the moment you enter the large foyer, you can see the open floor plan into the spacious living/great room.  Sliders to the back of the home offer a clear view of the large, fenced backyard. The kitchen features spacious, espresso wood cabinets and granite countertops. The large master bedroom includes an en-suite with an oversized walk-in closet and a large shower. The bathrooms all have stunning white quartz countertops. The Chatham Walk community features walking trails, a community pool with a cabana, a playground, a dog park for your four-legged family members, and open green space for a game of kickball. Schedule your showing today before this one is gone!
